ue et réfléchir !  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 4aChemistry. 7aSCIENCE / Chemistry / General.2bisacsh1 aBazile, Didier, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBerthier, Serge, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBetbeder, Didier, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aBetbeder, Didier, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBigot, Bernard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFattal, Elias, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aFattal, Elias, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKlein, Étienne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLe Mercier, Thierry, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLivage, Jacques, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLévy, Didier, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMartin, François, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNavarro, Christophe, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNesslany, Fabrice, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOlivier, Danièle, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPerrin, Jean-François, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRabu, Pierre, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRigny, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSamorì, Paolo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSéby, Fabienne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTillement, Olivier, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc